1.  Create a web page to process customer data using local storage.
	
		a.  Read the following details from the user
					1.   Customer Name
					2.   Joined Date
					3.   Favourite Color

	Hint:  Use Forms 2.0 controls suitable for the above requirement
					
					
2.   Create another page to display customer details

	a.  Apply page background color when page is opened
	b.  Display Welcome message based on the user name in heading
	c.   Display Joined Date -- details in the paragraph. 
		 
Hint:  If data does not exists,  background color  white /  welcome to Guest user / Date is empty
